      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:AdamNussbaum.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/AdamNussbaum.jpg/330px-AdamNussbaum.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/AdamNussbaum.jpg/500px-AdamNussbaum.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/AdamNussbaum.jpg/960px-AdamNussbaum.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:AdamNussbaum.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Adam Nussbaum, 2007 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adam_Nussbaum\">Adam Nussbaum</a>, (born November 29, 1955)<br />\nan American jazz drummer.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Category:Adam_Nussbaum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Adam Nussbaum performing at a jazz festival in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Puerto_Rico\">Puerto Rico</a>. Image by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.flickr.com/people/54873598@N00\">Jaime Olmo</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barceloneta,_Puerto_Rico\">Barceloneta, Puerto Rico</a>, June 02, 2007, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"externa